# Weather Sunscreen App - Project Structure Guide

## Entry Points & Core Architecture
- **Main Entry**: [index.ts](mdc:index.ts) → [App.tsx](mdc:App.tsx) → [src/navigation/index.tsx](mdc:src/navigation/index.tsx)
- **App Structure**: React Native + Expo app with TypeScript
- **Navigation**: Bottom tab navigation with 4 main screens (Weather, UV Index, Forecast, Tracker)

## Key Directories & Files

### Core Application
- [App.tsx](mdc:App.tsx) - Root component with context providers
- [src/navigation/index.tsx](mdc:src/navigation/index.tsx) - Main navigation configuration
- [src/context/](mdc:src/context/) - React Context for state management
  - [WeatherContext.tsx](mdc:src/context/WeatherContext.tsx) - Weather data and location state
  - [SunscreenContext.tsx](mdc:src/context/SunscreenContext.tsx) - Sunscreen tracking state

### Screens & Components
- [src/navigation/screens/](mdc:src/navigation/screens/) - Main app screens
  - [WeatherScreen.tsx](mdc:src/navigation/screens/WeatherScreen.tsx) - Current weather display
  - [UVIndexScreen.tsx](mdc:src/navigation/screens/UVIndexScreen.tsx) - UV index information
  - [ForecastScreen.tsx](mdc:src/navigation/screens/ForecastScreen.tsx) - Weather forecast
  - [SunscreenTrackerScreen.tsx](mdc:src/navigation/screens/SunscreenTrackerScreen.tsx) - Sunscreen usage tracking
- [src/components/](mdc:src/components/) - Reusable UI components
  - [icons/](mdc:src/components/icons/) - Custom icon components
  - [glass/](mdc:src/components/glass/) - Liquid glass UI components

### Services & Data
- [src/services/](mdc:src/services/) - API and business logic services
  - [weatherService.ts](mdc:src/services/weatherService.ts) - Weather data fetching
  - [openMeteoService.ts](mdc:src/services/openMeteoService.ts) - OpenMeteo API integration
  - [locationService.ts](mdc:src/services/locationService.ts) - Location handling
  - [sunscreenService.ts](mdc:src/services/sunscreenService.ts) - Sunscreen tracking logic

### Native Modules
- [modules/weather-native-module/](mdc:modules/weather-native-module/) - Native iOS/Android weather functionality
  - [index.ts](mdc:modules/weather-native-module/index.ts) - Cross-platform native module interface

### Configuration
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Dependencies and scripts
- [app.json](mdc:app.json) - Expo configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- [ios/](mdc:ios/) - iOS native code and configuration

## Development Workflow
- Use `bun start` for development server
- Use `bun run ios` for iOS simulator
- Use `bun run android` for Android emulator
